Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.95,0:01:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你 由太郎\N一定要保護好神聖的靈藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.99,0:01:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕不能讓他們得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.83,0:01:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.56,0:02:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可否知道你的芳名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.90,0:02:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真田忍者頭目 洩矢御沙薙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.87,0:02:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請原諒我的無禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.18,0:02:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了 就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是博士的筆記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.72,0:02:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.85,0:02:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普通石頭嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.82,0:02:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩樣東西就是線索了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.46,0:02:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第八十四話\N真田忍者群與靈藥\N頭目御沙薙的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.80,0:02:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過…為什麼德國軍人\N會攻擊漢斯老爹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不是很瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.34,0:02:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他們是奉德國命令行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.68,0:02:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不應該做出那種\N類似暗殺行動的事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.51,0:02:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…他們到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.25,0:02:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險的德國軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神秘靈藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.16,0:03:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被搞糊塗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.56,0:03:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣 由太郎 有什麼線索嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.56,0:03:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼找線索呀\N這本筆記上的字像蚯蚓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是蚯蚓啦 是拉丁語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.24,0:03:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是\N博士想到萬一筆記被奪走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.51,0:03:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故意使用難以理解的語言的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來那不是德語啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.98,0:03:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這本筆記留給我的愛徒\N冢山由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.39,0:03:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請原諒為了避免波及到你\N而隱瞞你此事的我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.03,0:03:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當你看到這一段時\N我可能已經出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不管我的性命是否還在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.67,0:03:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在記載的這件事\N我無論如何必需傳達給你知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.08,0:03:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾年前\N我調查有關東方的文獻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.08,0:04:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到了三百年左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.85,0:04:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在日本傳教的葡萄牙傳教士\N帶回的舊地圖跟小石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位傳教士的日記上面記載
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古代希臘神話中被稱為\N尼克塔爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.00,0:04:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,印度神話中被稱為亞姆裏答\N的傳說中神聖的靈藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.70,0:04:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是長生不老的秘藥\N還存在日本地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.48,0:04:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎 如你所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,近來微生物學的發達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.68,0:04:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,導致傳染病的源頭\N病原菌陸陸續續被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.26,0:04:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我驗證了那個成果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.12,0:04:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使盡所有辦法來調查\N跟靈藥相關的文獻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.83,0:04:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得到一個假設
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.77,0:04:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈藥可能含有\N抑制病原菌活動的未知物質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.24,0:05:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事\N已經不是單純的傳說與童話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.68,0:05:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它還藏有重寫醫學歷史\N開拓醫學新時代的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.76,0:05:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害 如果能夠證實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.33,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼那麼厲害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.76,0:05:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.46,0:05:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分析靈藥的成份\N就可開發出神奇的特效藥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.44,0:05:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼做的話\N許多得了不治之癥的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以獲救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.28,0:05:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那古代地圖確實是\N記載靈藥所在地的東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.08,0:05:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說 想奪取地圖的\N德國軍人也想得到靈藥了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍人跟藥物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.39,0:05:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點連結不起來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.46,0:05:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.76,0:05:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是可怕的魔手正向我逼近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們黑騎士團的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.80,0:06:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑騎士團？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.44,0:06:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中世紀以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.21,0:06:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以歐洲為中心擴大勢力的\N秘密組織黑騎士團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.75,0:06:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其組成份子廣泛 軍人\N科學家、政客、大商賈皆有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.25,0:06:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人說他們全是由\N各界的精英份子組成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的目的是統治全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.63,0:06:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想藉由奇跡的特效藥\N產生的利益來得到龐大資金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.36,0:06:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,達成支配世界的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.57,0:06:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬一靈藥落入他們手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.54,0:06:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將成為把\N世界導向混亂的災難種子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.48,0:06:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.72,0:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們身為德國軍人\N卻又隸屬於黑騎士團之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.45,0:06:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後他們就跑到日本來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.03,0:06:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想統治全世界這念頭\N太驚人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.26,0:07:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑 這種惡劣傢伙\N怎麼可以讓他們得到靈藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說歸說 沒地圖的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.34,0:07:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.54,0:07:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像連博士都無法解讀呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.51,0:07:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在筆記的最後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寫著一段奇怪的日本話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.75,0:07:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順著天流往上追溯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個州羽之海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四龍月上昇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神渡的時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通往虎口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.69,0:07:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷失於無明黑暗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.06,0:07:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖觀音之手所指之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.36,0:07:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將前往\N大富士的山麓之道打開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.24,0:07:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一段文句是\N我們真田的遠祖就流傳下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.41,0:07:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是黑騎士團\N應該知道這代表什麼意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.59,0:08:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 靈藥的所在\N就寫在這裏面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.09,0:08:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面還有一行\N墨水滲開來 看不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.23,0:08:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重點是 那是指哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天流逆流之處…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,州羽之海嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.11,0:08:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,州羽 不會是指諏訪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫做御沙薙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.65,0:08:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們一族對靈藥似乎很瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.35,0:08:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的瞭解只維持到\N戰國亂世文獻散失掉為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.83,0:08:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也因此 至今連我們\N都無法解開最後的謎題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.87,0:08:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我想跟全球消息網的\N黑騎士團聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個提議應該不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.04,0:08:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以幫你們提早達成目的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.68,0:09:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的目的\N我不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.89,0:09:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都這時候了你還不相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.96,0:09:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼好吧 當我沒有提議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.26,0:09:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御沙薙小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.59,0:09:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果惹你不高興了\N還請多見諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.37,0:09:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 我也坦白說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.10,0:09:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了創造我們理想的新世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.31,0:09:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潛伏各界的同志起義的時間\N依我們判斷還要十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是如你所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.92,0:09:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是我們可以得到靈藥\N時間就只需五年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.92,0:09:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 三年就可以起義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.59,0:09:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…有一點我想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.49,0:09:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對你而言靈藥是祖先的寶物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.13,0:09:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的可以不在乎地\N把靈藥分一半給我們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.97,0:09:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 全部給你們也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.84,0:09:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.51,0:09:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想要什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.95,0:10:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要這個國家 日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.68,0:10:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 左之助說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.16,0:10:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天流 表示天龍川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.29,0:10:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,州羽之海 一定是指諏訪湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.36,0:10:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…四龍是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.13,0:10:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.93,0:10:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月亮昇起 神渡是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.54,0:10:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑騎士團已經開始行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.84,0:10:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能落後他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去諏訪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.64,0:11:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭目回來了！開門！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.94,0:11:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些外國人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們來做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.45,0:11:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是忍者嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.09,0:11:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好貧窮的山中猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 他們的神情不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點破綻也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別講廢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.00,0:12:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.97,0:12:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 現在我們真田忍者群\N跟黑騎士團締結同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.48,0:12:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劃入梅爾達斯中尉指揮下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.81,0:12:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 怎麼這樣 頭目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.01,0:12:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肅靜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.78,0:12:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,違抗頭目決定的人是何下場\N你們該不會忘記族規吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.30,0:12:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,州羽之海…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.17,0:12:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諏訪湖確實像海洋一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來是來了 以後怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.84,0:12:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼前的線索只能\N讓我們知道應該在這一帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.48,0:12:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諏訪地方太廣大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.28,0:12:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諏訪神社呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本地最有歷史的諏訪神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.76,0:13:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該會有關靈藥的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓狗多跑跑總會撞上柱子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說我們是狗嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撞上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實是大柱子呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.57,0:13:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你在幹什麼 這邊這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.55,0:13:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神聖的靈藥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.06,0:13:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傳說我從沒聽說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.90,0:13:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有用…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.43,0:13:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來只好試其它地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.54,0:13:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,廟公 請問那柱子是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是神柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.45,0:14:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才來的時候 對面也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是神木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.38,0:14:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這裏看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.55,0:14:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊也有 那邊也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.26,0:14:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛好在四個角落\N全部合起來是四棵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.19,0:14:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諏訪神社應該是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.26,0:14:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們本宮、上社前宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.00,0:14:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上湖對岸的\N下社的春宮與秋宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.67,0:14:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四宮合起來總稱為諏訪大社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.48,0:14:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這四神社各自有四根御柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.38,0:14:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四根？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.95,0:14:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是\N從八岳深山鋸來16根巨木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.72,0:14:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越過平野高山運過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這叫做御柱祭呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.46,0:14:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是\N很勇敢雄壯的一個祭神儀式呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.57,0:14:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時來了不少人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.04,0:14:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四根…四龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.31,0:15:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個御柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.48,0:15:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不覺得看起來像龍嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.32,0:15:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟一些地方信仰對照來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.52,0:15:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些地方風俗是把\N柱子與巨木當龍神來崇拜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.13,0:15:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的話 四龍\N所謂的四隻龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.00,0:15:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可能代表四根御柱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.17,0:15:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然說\N看起來只像沒用的大釘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這孩子有點發燒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果它是龍的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.85,0:15:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月亮昇起 神渡時\N又是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神渡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.69,0:15:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指御神渡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.56,0:15:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在冬天寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.89,0:15:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上社祭拜的建御名方神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.77,0:16:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會去見下社祭拜的女神\N八阪常女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.81,0:16:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諏訪湖湖面大半都結冰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.38,0:16:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是冰面呢 轟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.25,0:16:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發出巨響磅的一聲\N湖面發生龜裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.19,0:16:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就稱為神渡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.36,0:16:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯了\N靈藥就在諏訪湖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.03,0:16:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是神社跟諏訪湖這麼大耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.97,0:16:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等到神渡時刻\N應該可以縮小範圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.07,0:16:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.24,0:16:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.84,0:16:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神渡是在冬天耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎 你不吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.57,0:17:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也難怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.97,0:17:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前宮跟下社的兩個神社\N得到的線索都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.41,0:17:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等於又回到起點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拿到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.21,0:17:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不甘願的話就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.25,0:17:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛呀\N這樣失魂落魄的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.62,0:17:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍者！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.53,0:17:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.60,0:17:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.81,0:17:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到這時代還有這種高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們乖一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.02,0:17:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.19,0:18:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都御庭番眾\N卷町操來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.93,0:18:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現得正是時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.41,0:18:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番眾算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.75,0:18:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番眾\N你們竟敢跟我們為敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情不會善了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.39,0:18:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們該知道忍者的行規的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真田忍者群？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.70,0:18:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豐臣在大阪滅亡之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.60,0:18:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們就在信濃的山中\N築起自己的獨立國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.11,0:18:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從幕府時代開始\N御庭番眾就有監視他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.95,0:19:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近他們行跡可疑\N我們才展開調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.15,0:19:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果又跟緋村會合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.65,0:19:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.59,0:19:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.92,0:19:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是神谷道場的門生\N冢山由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.69,0:19:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本行是醫生哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.89,0:19:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭 阿薰 我還是學生啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.03,0:19:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫卷町操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外表看來像美麗的京都小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我是御庭番眾的頭目哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.34,0:19:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.91,0:19:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以叫我魅力女孩小操嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在意啦 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.41,0:19:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是普通忍者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.85,0:19:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有人稱她是妖怪鼬鼠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說誰是妖怪鼬鼠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就說普通鼬鼠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.52,0:19:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼這樣 我哪裏像鼬鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.82,0:19:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傀太 幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.96,0:19:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們拿命去博鬥時\N你卻答應那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.87,0:19:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算有族規\N我還是無法心服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.14,0:20:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然要我們聽外人命令\N還把靈藥交給他們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的使命是保護它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.41,0:20:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為此\N我們的爸爸跟爺爺才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.15,0:20:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時代已經改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.65,0:20:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.78,0:20:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙的處刑 交給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真田忍者來攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定跟靈藥有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.76,0:20:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從他們對靈藥有所瞭解\N這一點看來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.53,0:20:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找不出頭緒的我們就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好出奇不意攻擊他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.50,0:20:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我大概知道\N真田的碉堡在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.41,0:20:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是從剛才到現在\N你們講的靈藥是什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.18,0:21:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次相當的棘手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.62,0:21:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說是叛徒\N失去這麼優秀的戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我衷心致上我的同情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.56,0:21:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不需要你的同情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.59,0:21:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我很在意讓戒太受傷\N的紅髮劍客一行人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.83,0:21:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙先前我也見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.40,0:21:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.47,0:21:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們跟漢斯博士有關聯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.87,0:21:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們出現在諏訪表示\N他們也有某些線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.68,0:21:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我猜解開\N最後之謎的關鍵也在其中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.48,0:21:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就抓住他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.02,0:21:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 有更好的辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.52,0:21:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾脆\N讓那些傢伙找到「靈藥」吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.66,0:22:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.60,0:22:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上請多小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.90,0:22:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.60,0:22:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵達京都\N請轉告翁爺爺別操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.14,0:22:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標是真田碉堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.51,0:22:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.35,0:22:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅髮 臉頰有十字刀疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.66,0:22:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯 就是那個男人

